snippet.title: Etna Crimson【NIJISANJI / にじさんじ】
snippet.description:
DUARRR!! Etna.. sanjou!! Hello everyone!! My name is Etna Crimson, you can call me Etna! Etna is a half-super human, that also was a hero. Etna is now in NIJISANJI as a Liver (live streamer) to make sure that you all are happy! Seeing people happy makes Etna feel that justice and virtue have been served, and that is happiness for Etna! Etna may be a bit clumsy, but Etna will keep trying! Berjuaang! Buurrn! Dhuaarr! Kebakarr!! Nice to meet you all! Yoosh, Etnarimasu~!
